fields.name: proc_bhp1/etap
fields.declaration:
class Etap(base_form):
    from schlib.schdjangoext.widgets import ImgFileInput
    obrazek1 = forms.ImageField(label='Obrazek 1', required=False, widget=ImgFileInput)
    dopasuj1 = forms.BooleanField(label='', required=False)
    obrazek2 = forms.ImageField(label='Obrazek 2', required=False, widget=ImgFileInput)
    dopasuj2 = forms.BooleanField(label='', required=False)
    obrazek3 = forms.ImageField(label='Obrazek 3', required=False, widget=ImgFileInput)
    dopasuj3 = forms.BooleanField(label='', required=False)
    obrazek4 = forms.ImageField(label='Obrazek 4', required=False, widget=ImgFileInput)
    dopasuj4 = forms.BooleanField(label='', required=False)    
    opis = forms.CharField(label='Opis', widget=forms.Textarea, required=False)
    view_type = forms.CharField(max_length=16) 
    
return Etap
